OL,3,CCall for Guernsey's government to put
OL,4,Ctax break on charitable donations
OL,6,FA charity leader has criticised
OL,7,Fgovernment for not doing enough to
OL,8,Fsupport local good causes.
OL,10,FThe outgoing Vice President of the
OL,11,FAssociation of Guernsey Charities
OL,12,F(AGC), Peter Rose, announced he was
OL,13,Fstepping down earlier this month after
OL,14,F11 years with the group and wants a
OL,15,Ftax break on donations to help
OL,16,Fgenerate funds.
