OL,3,CCall for Guernsey's government to put
OL,4,Ctax break on charitable donations
OL,6,FHe says: "If you put money into it you
OL,7,Fwill reap the benefits. We did a
OL,8,Freview of how effective charitable
OL,9,Fgiving would be if there was gift aid
OL,10,Fand they reckon that the social return
OL,11,Fon investment, the benefit you get
OL,12,Fover and above donations was two and a
OL,13,Fhalf times.
OL,15,F"So you get two and a half the bang
OL,16,Ffor your buck if you gift aid to
OL,17,Fcharities because charities do things
OL,18,Fmore efficiently: they're run by
OL,19,Fvolunteers, whereas government
OL,20,Fpolicies are far more general."
