OL,3,CCall for Guernsey's government to put
OL,4,Ctax break on charitable donations
OL,6,FA gift aid scheme is already used in
OL,7,Fthe United Kingdom which means
OL,8,Fcharities and community sports clubs
OL,9,Fcan claim an extra 25p from the
OL,10,Fgovernment for every #1 that is
OL,11,Fdonated.
OL,13,FThere are also calls for more focus on
OL,14,Fbusinesses.
OL,16,FCharity Director Bella Farrell says:
OL,17,F"In a recent Health and Social Care
OL,18,Fsurvey, only 1% of the private sector
OL,19,Fsupported the third sector.
