OL,3,CCall for Guernsey's government to put
OL,4,Ctax break on charitable donations
OL,6,F"That sounds ridiculous and there was
OL,7,F27% or 29% who in some way touched the
OL,8,Fthird sector but we should be seeing
OL,9,F80% or 100%, so we should not just be
OL,10,Ffocusing on what the government can
OL,11,Fdo, I think that's the easy question."
OL,13,FThe Vice President of Guernsey's
OL,14,FPolicy and Resources Committee, Deputy
OL,15,FHeidi Soulsby, says: "It is a subject
OL,16,Fthat Peter feels very strongly about
OL,17,Fbut the AGC has not raised the subject
OL,18,Fof gift aid for some time which means
OL,19,Fit has not been looked at this term.
